{"id":558777,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/【立此存照】江泽民、钱其琛与华山医院的罗生门/","date":"2017-05-11T07:22:42Z","modified":"2017-05-11T07:22:42Z","title":"【立此存照】江泽民、钱其琛与华山医院的罗生门","content":"<p>2017年5月10日，上海实验学校在其<a href=\"http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/RP1vajpBIdluWefg0FHszw\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">官方微信公号上</a>为近日流传的江泽民病危传言低调地辟了一次“谣”，称<strong>该校校长接到了江泽民的校庆贺电</strong>：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_558778\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/上海市实验学校.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558778\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/上海市实验学校.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"477\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/上海市实验学校.jpg 1084w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/上海市实验学校-300x272.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/上海市实验学校-768x697.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/上海市实验学校-1024x930.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">微信公号“上海市实验学校”文章截图</span></p></div>\n<p>很快，新浪微博上就已无法搜索“<strong>江爷爷</strong>”这个关键词。网传江泽民“病危”期间所在的“<strong>华山医院</strong>”，近日也已被微博列为搜索禁词。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_558783\" style=\"width: 460px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/江爷爷.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558783\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/江爷爷.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"450\" height=\"187\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/江爷爷.jpg 1394w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/江爷爷-300x124.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/江爷爷-768x318.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/江爷爷-1024x425.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 450px) 100vw, 450px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">新浪微博搜索结果截图</span></p></div>\n<blockquote><p><strong>相关阅读</strong>：<a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/05/%e3%80%90%e6%95%8f%e6%84%9f%e8%af%8d%e5%ba%93%e3%80%91%e5%be%90%e6%99%93%e5%86%ac%e9%81%ad%e5%b0%81%e6%9d%80%e7%9b%b8%e5%85%b3%e3%80%81%ef%bc%88%e6%b1%9f%e6%b3%bd%e6%b0%91%ef%bc%89%e5%8d%8e%e5%b1%b1/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">【敏感词库】徐晓冬遭封杀相关、（江泽民）华山医院</a></p></blockquote>\n<p>就在上海实验学校为江“辟谣”的当天，新华社发布了钱其琛逝世的消息，其中短暂地出现了“<strong>华山医院</strong>”的身影。“凤凰资讯”转发新华社通稿时，<strong>最初的版本是“钱其琛今日在上海华山医院去世”</strong>。截至发稿时，所有通稿都已改为“在北京逝世”，<strong>但从凤凰资讯网页的谷歌快照上，还是可以在 meta 信息中看出最早的“华山医院”内容</strong>：</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_558779\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯1.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558779\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯1.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"76\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯1.jpg 2386w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯1-300x38.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯1-768x97.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯1-1024x130.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">凤凰资讯谷歌快照网页源码截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_558780\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯2.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558780\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯2.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"92\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯2.jpg 2392w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯2-300x46.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯2-768x118.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯2-1024x158.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">凤凰资讯谷歌快照网页源码截图</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_558781\" style=\"width: 610px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯3.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558781\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯3.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"600\" height=\"64\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯3.jpg 2078w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯3-300x32.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯3-768x81.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯3-1024x108.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">上述网页的快照保存于 格林威治时间2017年5月10日11时26分</span></p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_558782\" style=\"width: 510px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯4.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558782\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯4.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"479\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯4.jpg 1422w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯4-300x287.jpg 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯4-768x736.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/凤凰资讯4-1024x981.jpg 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">凤凰资讯修改后的版本</span></p></div>\n<p>所以，这次的乌龙到底是凤凰资讯的报道错误，还是新华社出于某种原因紧急修改了通稿内容？网上流传的华山医院周边戒严，是否是由于钱其琛的缘故？</p>\n<p>又是一桩罗生门。</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_558784\" style=\"width: 410px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/钱其琛.jpg\"><img class=\"wp-image-558784\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/钱其琛.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"400\" height=\"652\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/钱其琛.jpg 1084w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/钱其琛-184x300.jpg 184w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/钱其琛-768x1253.jpg 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/05/钱其琛-628x1024.jpg 628w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 400px) 100vw, 400px\" /></a><p class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span style=\"color: #808080;\">有记者在微博就此质问新华社</span></p></div>\n","author":980,"categories":[18271,18270,18269,27949],"tags":[18847,17263,25380,18396]}